            "id": "typewriter-explode",
            "title": "Typewriter: Exploding Countdown",
            "description": "An example of a typewriter animation using Motion for React's Typewriter component. In this demo, the Typewriter uses a natural typing animation to animate to the latest value, and then explodes the text using splitText.",
